fields.description:
h5.Description:
The tizen module in the module's folder should be removed as we are not supporting tizen from 3.3.0.

I am not actually sure for what purpose it does exists.

Path for the module : Titanium/modules/tizen/tizen/3.0.0
fields.summary: Tizen: Remove Tizen module from the Titanium SDK

comments.body:
The module was I was seeing was present from the previous SDK versions which supported tizen . 

The latest 3.3.0 SDK at the time of opening the ticket does download any tizen module.

Closing.
